cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image datasets and utilizes deep generative models for anomaly detection and downstream classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves unsupervised learning, which suggests categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of normalizing flow models and convolutional neural networks suggests categories such as cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
